criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  adult patients >=18 years of age;

          -  chronic renal anemia;

          -  on dialysis (hemodialysis or peritoneal dialysis) therapy for at least 3 months;

          -  receiving sc epoetin alfa or beta for at least 3 months prior to the run-in period.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  women who are pregnant, breastfeeding or using unreliable birth control methods;

          -  use of any investigational drug within 30 days preceding the run-in phase, or during
             the run-in or study treatment period.
